## cd /Users/hedley/Documents/workspace/lost_release/Common
## svn log --search yumiao -l 100 -v
## svn log --verbose -r 97771
export LANG="en_US.UTF-8"
p="/Users/hedley/Desktop/dump/excel-check"
url="http://yandeli@svn.super-chameleon.com:8822/svn/lost/Source/branches_ptr/Common/xlsx_config/gameConfig/"
output="/Users/hedley/.lost/.log/temp"
cd /Users/hedley/Documents/workspace/lost_ptr/Common/xlsx_config/gameConfig
query=$1;
arr=(${query// / })
for vesion in ${arr[@]}; do
svn log --verbose -r $vesion >> $output
for file in `svn log --verbose -r $vesion | grep 'xlsx$' | awk '{print $NF}' `; do name=${file##*/};
new=$p/$name".new.xlsx" new2=$p/$name".new.csv"
old=$p/$name".old.xlsx" old2=$p/$name".old.csv"
svn export -r $vesion $url$name $new --force
svn export -r $(( $vesion-1 )) $url$name $old --force
/usr/local/bin/in2csv $new | perl -pe's#"[^"]*"#$&=~y/,/_/r#ge' > $new2
/usr/local/bin/in2csv $old | perl -pe's#"[^"]*"#$&=~y/,/_/r#ge' > $old2
echo "r"$vesion" "$name >> $output sed -n '2p;' $new2 >> $output echo '========================================================================' >> $output
sdiff -B -s -W -w 500 $old2 $new2 | column -t >> $output
echo >> $output
if [ `sdiff -B -s -W -w 500 $old2 $new2 | column -t | grep -c '\|'` -ge 1 ]; then
sed -n '2p;' $new2 > ./temp
if [ `sed 's/[^,]//g' ./temp | awk '{ print length }'` -le 50 ]; then
sdiff -B -s -W -w 500 $old2 $new2 | tr '|' '\n' | column -t | perl -pe 's|(.*)<$|\-$1|; s|^>\s*([^ ]*)|\+$1|' > ./temp
sed -n '2p;' $new2 >> ./temp
perl -i -pe 's#(?<=,)(?=,)#_#g; s#^,#_,#; s#, *$#,_#; ' ./temp rs -c',' -C' ' -T < ./temp | column -t >> $output echo >> $output echo >> $output
fi; fi;
done; echo >> $output echo >> $output echo >> $output echo >> $output echo >> $output echo >> $output echo >> $output done;
echo 'done.' >> $output
rm -rf ./temp
